title: Hour 3 - Sean Salisbury and Sam Amick (06-29-20)
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Sean Salisbury and Sam Amick (06-29-20)
description:
Sean Salisbury talked to Dan about Cam Newton joining the patriots. Sean feels its a positive because now you can add some things that Tom Brady didn't bring to the team. Sam Amick Says it only takes 1 case to mess up the entire restart of the NBA.
